$PROBLEM    ADPO benchmark - NONMEM
$ABBR DERIV2=NO 
$INPUT   ID TIME AMT DV EVID BQL WT
$DATA      ..\..\..\data_sim.csv IGNORE=@
$SUBROUTINE ADVAN6 TOL=7
$MODEL
  COMP=(DEPOT,DEFDOSE)
  COMP=(CENTRAL,NODOSE,DEFOBS)

$PK      
  CWT = WT/70 

  TVVMAX= THETA(1)   
  VMAX=TVVMAX*EXP(ETA(1)) 
  TVKM = THETA(2)
  KM = TVKM  
  TVV2=THETA(3) 
  V2=TVV2    
  TVKA=THETA(4) 
  KA=TVKA   

  SC = V2
$ERROR    
  IPRED = F
  IOBS = F*EXP(EPS(2)) + EPS(1)
  Y=F*EXP(EPS(2)) + EPS(1)
$DES
  CONC = A(2)/SC
  DADT(1) = -KA*A(1)
  DADT(2) =  KA*A(1)-VMAX*CONC/(KM+CONC) 


$THETA   
  (100,4000,10000)	; THETA(1) VMAX UNITS =  mass/time
  (100,1000,3000)	; THETA(2) KM UNITS = mass/volume
  (1,50) 		; THETA(3) V  UNITS = volume
  (0.01,1.2,3) 		; THETA(4) KA UNITS = 1/time    



  ;; Start OMEGA5
$OMEGA  
  0.1		; ETA(1) ETA ON VMAX
$SIGMA     
  (1) ;; EPS(1) ADDITIVE
  (0.3) ;; EPS(2) PROPORTIONAL
$SIM (2345) ONLYSIM 
$TABLE ID TIME AMT IOBS EVID WT FILE=../../../OUT_0_0_0_0.DAT NOPRINT NOHEADER NOAPPEND
  ;;; Model Identifier =  0,0,0,0
$TABLE ID VMAX KM V2 KA FIRSTONLY NOAPPEND NOPRINT FILE= ../../../PARMS_0_0_0_0.DAT
